overview: The Quireboys are 35 Years Young, We join the fans, the press and the band onstage and behind the scenes as they unleash 100% of Pure Gypsy Rock n Roll Live at their Sold out Anniversary show @ 02 Kentish Town Forum, London. A true English heritage Rock Band in it's prime and not looking to stop anytime soon...
title: The Quireboys - 35 & Live
